Munhu yoyose yoyomtogola Mwana wa Mulungu kana usindila uwo muna umoyo wake. Munhu yoyose yoyolema kumuhuwila Mulungu, komtenda Mulungu yawe mvwizi, kwaviya hahuwile usindila uja Mulungu woulavile kumsonhela Mwanage.
Uno uwo ukalangama uwo, Mulungu kaching'ha ugima wa siku zose, na ugima uwo wowoneka mwa Mwanage.
Munhu yoyose yeli na Mwana wa Mulungu kana ugima uwo, na munhu yoyose yelibule Mwana wa Mulungu kabule ugima uwo.
Noyandika yano yose kumwenu mweye womumuhuwila Mwana wa Mulungu, muladi muvimanye kuwa munawo ugima wa siku zose.
Chino icho chochilonda kumsondelela Mulungu, hachimuhulika one chiya chochose chochilonda fana viyolonda yeye.
